title: Ep. 45 - Best Of Part 2
description:
The guys are on vacation, so they've picked some of their favorite segments, conversations, and moments from the last 6 months. Come and have a good time with us.


This episode features @toddmccomas, @PatMcAfeeshow, @Digz, @nickmaraldo, @tyschmit, @BostonConnr, @VivalaZito, @evanfoxy, and @baileymccomas.
